Shotcuts
------------
Command + option + J        -> Developer Mode in Chrome
Cmd+Option+U                -> source Code
CMD + Shift + P             -> Format Document
Shift + Option + A          -> Multiline Commments 
Command + /                 -> Single Line Comment




Formatter
------------
Add Extension "Prettier - Code formatter"
Add Extension "Bracket Pair Colorization Toggler"




Install Node
-------------
node -v
brew install node
npm -v




Configure Project Using npm
-----------------------------
npm init -y
Or
npm init

npm install -D parcel     (for Dev dependency)
npm install parcel     (for normal dependency)




